  <p>
    
    <milestone facs="3" n="33r" unit="folio"/>
    <lb n="1"/><seg function="incipit">makā-t-tiraḻ<pc>-</pc>āy iṟukkiṟatiṉālē tamakku-p pōka-k kūṭat<pc>’</pc> iruntāl Anta-p piḷḷaikaḷukkuḷḷē</seg> cattu
    <lb n="2" break="no"/>vayacilē miñci-k keṭṭikkāṟar<pc>-</pc>āy irukkiṟa cila Aṇ-piḷḷaikaḷai-k kuṟiccu-t tamuṭaiya vaca
    <lb n="3" break="no"/>ttilē-y irukkiṟa cipa-mālai yāṉāl-um curūpam ākilum Aṟciyacīṣa paṇṭam eṉkilum Avar
    <lb n="4" break="no"/>kaḷ kaiyilē kuṭutt<pc>’</pc> aṉuppuvār Appōtu Anta-p piḷḷaikaḷ Avar kaṭṭaḷai-y iṭṭatiṉ paṭi
    <lb n="5" break="no"/>yē Anta viyātikkāṟar Aṇṭaiyilē pōy vicuvācam<pc>-</pc>āy vēṇṭi-k-koṇṭatiṉālē viyāti-ku
    
    <milestone facs="4" n="33v" unit="folio" break="no"/>
    <lb n="1"/>ṇam<pc>-</pc>ākum Inta-p piṟakāram<pc>-</pc>āka Anta-c ciṟu piḷḷaikaḷai-k koṇṭu It-taṉai putumaikaḷai-p paṇṇiviccu
    <lb n="2" break="no"/>k koṇṭuvanta Aṟciyacīṣa cavēriyār Anta-c cīrmaiyilē vayacu ceṉṟ<pc>’</pc> irukkiṟavaṉum<pc>-</pc>āy
    <lb n="3" break="no"/>makā-cāstiṟiyum<pc>-</pc>āy irukkiṟa Oru pirāmaṇaṉukku Ellārum Āccariya-p paṭa-t takkat<pc>’</pc> āka Upatēca
    <lb n="4" break="no"/>ñ colli ñāṉasnāṉaṅ kuṭuttār Ituvum Oru putumai pōlē Iruntutu At<pc>’</pc> ēṉ eṉṟāl An
    <lb n="5" break="no"/>tap pirāmaṇaṉ āṉavaṉ maṟṟa-p pirāmaṇarukkuḷḷē <gap reason="ellipsis"/> pirāmaṇaṉum-āy iruntutum allāmal
    
    <milestone facs="5" n="34r" unit="folio"/>
    <lb n="1"/>caṟuvēśvaraṉ<pc>-</pc>uṭaiya vētattiṉ pērilē makā-p-pakai-y<pc>-</pc>āy iruntāṉ Avaṉ kiṟistuvaṉ-āy-p <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
    <lb n="2" break="no"/>ṉ atukku-p piṟpāṭu Aykkiyāṉikaḻukkuḷḷē Aṉēkam pērkaḷ Avaṉ mukāntiram<pc>-</pc>āka-p piḻai
    <lb n="3" break="no"/>ccu-t tirumpi-k kiṟīstuvarkaḷ<pc>-</pc>āy-p pōṉāṟkaḷ Ippaṭi putic<pc>-</pc>āy Anta tēcattilē ñāṉasnā
    <lb n="4" break="no"/>ṉam pettavarkaḷum munti-y irunta kiṟīstuvarkaḷum makā-t-tiraḷ<pc>-</pc>āy irukkiṟārkaḷ eṉṟu Aṟ
    <lb n="5" break="no"/>ciyacīṣa cavēriyār kaṇṭu tāmum tammōṭē kūṭa vant<pc>’</pc> irukkiṟa maṟṟa caṉṉāciyārum Atta
    
    <milestone facs="6" n="34v" unit="folio" break="no"/>
    <lb n="1"/>ṉai ceṉaṅkaḷai-p parāmarikkiṟatukku-p porāt<pc>’</pc> eṉṟu colli-y anta Ūrkaḷilē-y irukkiṟa kiṟī
    <lb n="2" break="no"/>stuvarkaḷukkuḷḷē-k kēṭṭikkāṟār<pc>-</pc>āy irukkiṟa cila pērkaḷai-t teriñcu koṇṭu Ovvoru
    <lb n="3" break="no"/>Ūrukku-t takkatu Oṉṟu Iraṇṭu mūṉṟu pērai vaiyccu-k kiṟīstuvarkaḷ-uṭaiya Avacaram<pc>-</pc>āṉa
    <lb n="4"/>kāriyaṅkaḷai parāmarikka-c colli-k kaṭ<choice><sic>ṭi</sic><corr>ṭa</corr></choice>ḷai-y iṭṭār Inta Oḻuṅkōṭē Avar kaṭ<choice><sic>ṭi</sic><corr>ṭa</corr></choice>ḷai
    <lb n="5" break="no"/>y iṭṭattukku-p piṟppāṭu tirumpa-k koṅkaṇa-tēcattukku-p pōy-c cila kurukkaḷai-k kūṭṭi-k
    
